com.pom.crimson.api

Class UserProfileControllerAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.api.UserProfileControllerAPI

  • public class UserProfileControllerAPI
extends java.lang.Object
    UserProfileControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to backend API and receive response from same. This uses Rest Assured library to create requests and fetch responses.
    Author:
    Sivaprakash Selvaraj, Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
